description:
Badner Halle, Rastatt, Germany, 1994

Celebrating the 40th anniversary of Chris Barber's professional band which was founded on May 31st 1954. The "1954 band" would play the first half followed by the current band in the 
second half. 

"Chris Barber's Jazz and Blues Band": CB, Pat Halcox (tp), Ian Wheeler (as, cl, harp), John Crocker (as, ts, cl), Johnny McCallum (bj, g), John Slaughter (g), Vic Pitt (b), Russell Gilbrook (dr)
